TaskTypeSchema.description:
JSON Schema for task type input / output fields.

Defines the form fields that lab users fill when submitting a task
(``input_schema``), or the output fields that staff/workers produce
(``output_schema``).

Example::

    {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
            "sample_id": {"type": "string", "title": "样品ID"},
            "plasmid": {"type": "object", "format": "file", "title": "质粒文件"}
        },
        "required": ["sample_id"]
    }
